### Development Setup
```bash
# Clone for development
git clone https://github.com/AmirHoseinBlue24/git-cli-tool.git
cd git-cli-tool

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .
```

